{"word":"H6749 - צָלַל - tsâlal - tsaw-lal' - Sink","slug":"H6749","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">צָלַל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>tsâlal"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>tsaw-lal'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Sink"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E6;&#x05DC;&#x05DC; - tsa&#x0302;lal</b> - <i>tsaw-lal'</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>tumble</i> down, that is, <i>settle</i> by a waving motion: - sink. Compare <a href=\"#/H6750\">H6750</a>, <a href=\"#/H6751\">H6751</a>."}]}